metadata.name: SLFPRTRT
metadata.description:
SLFPRTRT is a digital art object created in mid-2022. The symbolism of the speed of creation as a contrasting contrast to the depth of thought, strength and experience in the form of an interpretation of a well-known painting technique which symbolizes the idea of ​​​​its revolutionary symbol, on the one hand, and displays a simple portrait, on the other hand, with its simple idea, simple colors and simple possibilities.

The NFT comes with an original copy of the 4680 by 6650 pixel .TIFF image in 16-bit grayscale with a square pixel aspect ratio.
